  ],
  "remarks": "Etibar Eyyub founded and runs a network of companies including Coral Energy (later 2Rivers Group). Through this network of companies, he enables shipments and exports of Russian oil, notably from the Russian state owned oil-company Rosneft, by concealing the actual origin of the oil. In particular, the 2Rivers network controls and utilises a large proportion of the vessels in Russia’s so-called “shadow fleet”.",
